"translate it into your language, please contact the <ulink url=\"http://"
"developer.gnome.org/projects/gtp/\">GNOME Translation Project</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Gellir cyfieithu'r gwaith hwn i unrhyw iaith. Os hoffech chi ei gyfieithu "
"i'ch iaith eich hun, cysylltwch â <ulink url=\"http://developer.gnome.org/"
"projects/gtp/\">Phrosiect Cyfieithu GNOME</ulink>."

